cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the use of data markets to support AI, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the valuation and governance of data, which relates to database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of intrinsic and extrinsic value to determine the worth of data also relates to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cryptography (cs.CR).
